just thank You, Lord. Right now, I call

00:15:32.319 --> 00:15:34.949
healing over their bodies, from

00:15:34.959 --> 00:15:36.670
the top of their heads to the soles of

00:15:36.680 --> 00:15:40.069
their feet.

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:46.150
You are a healer and a

00:15:46.160 --> 00:15:48.749
deliverer.

00:15:48.759 --> 00:15:51.509
I thank You,

00:15:51.519 --> 00:15:54.470
Father, that You are our Great Physician.

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:56.269
I thank You, Lord, that You're

00:15:56.279 --> 00:15:57.790
creating miracles in their bodies right

00:15:57.800 --> 00:16:00.350
now.

00:16:05.680 --> 00:16:07.870
We thank You, Lord,

00:16:07.880 --> 00:16:10.309
that by the stripes of Jesus, they are

00:16:10.319 --> 00:16:12.829
healed and free. Thank You, Lord, for

00:16:12.839 --> 00:16:14.829
finances. We call

00:16:14.839 --> 00:16:16.870
in finances in the name of Jesus from

00:16:16.880 --> 00:16:18.790
the north, south, east, and west.

00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:20.550
We're calling in a great harvest

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:23.150
for their homes.

00:16:27.800 --> 00:16:29.790
We're

00:16:29.800 --> 00:16:31.350
calling those things that be not as

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:33.389
though they were, and we're speaking in

00:16:33.399 --> 00:16:35.710
the harvest right now. We speak to the

00:16:35.720 --> 00:16:37.870
mountain and tell it to be removed,

00:16:37.880 --> 00:16:40.670
and we have the mountain dissolve in faith. It

00:16:40.670 --> 00:16:40.680
is

00:16:40.680 --> 00:16:43.269
gone.

00:16:47.800 --> 00:16:50.670
The faith of a mustard seed moves a

00:16:50.680 --> 00:16:53.470
mountain, and I believe right now

00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:55.949
for everything they have need

00:16:55.959 --> 00:16:59.230
of, it is met in Jesus'name. We

00:16:59.240 --> 00:17:00.590
thank You, Lord, for marriages restored—homes full of joy and peace and kindness. Thank You, Lord, that their

00:17:00.590 --> 00:17:00.600
children

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:02.350
are

00:17:02.350 --> 00:17:02.360
blessed

00:17:02.360 --> 00:17:05.189
and whole

00:17:15.559 --> 00:17:17.470
in their

00:17:17.470 --> 00:17:17.480
minds—no

00:17:17.480 --> 00:17:20.150
more ADHD and autism.

00:17:27.400 --> 00:17:29.750
We give You all the glory,

00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:31.470
honor, and praise.

00:17:31.470 --> 00:17:31.480
I

00:17:31.480 --> 00:17:34.230
agree

00:17:34.240 --> 00:17:36.029
with them by faith: they are healed, set

00:17:36.039 --> 00:17:38.350
free, and delivered

00:17:38.360 --> 00:17:40.590
today. Amen

00:17:40.600 --> 00:17:43.110
and amen. Do you

00:17:43.120 --> 00:17:44.990
believe Jesus is your healer?

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:46.950
You've got to

00:17:46.960 --> 00:17:50.190
believe it; don't be begging, be believing.

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:52.590
I believe

00:17:52.600 --> 00:17:55.190
it's done.

00:17:58.200 --> 00:18:00.270
Thank

00:18:00.270 --> 00:18:00.280
you

00:18:00.280 --> 00:18:02.310
for watching.

00:18:02.320 --> 00:18:05.909
Please put a smile on your face

00:18:05.919 --> 00:18:08.950
and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:11.230
so much, and we love you. We will see

00:18:11.240 --> 00:18:13.710
you next time. Have a wonderful

00:18:13.720 --> 00:18:18.600
day. God bless you all. Bye-bye.

